{"tid":2031464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國會及行政當局中國委員會發表聲明：要求中国撤回香港国安法","createTime":"2020-05-23T12:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T03:56:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb29cd2b6e3965b328ec63cb3298ac9d614c0422","tid":2031464,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:01:48.000Z","msg":"星期五(5月22日)，美國國會及行政當局中國委員會（CECC）的主席和聯合主席，眾議員詹姆斯&middot;麥高文和參議員馬可&middot;魯比奧，就中國全國人大強制實施香港國家安全法發表聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/1CCDF5CD-D0B8-4357-A579-F3E3D5DFBDF8_w408_r0_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F1CCDF5CD-D0B8-4357-A579-F3E3D5DFBDF8_w408_r0_s.jpg&h=023979cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲明稱：&ldquo;我們與香港人民站在一起，譴責中華人民共和國全國人民代表大會作出的、在香港任意實施國家安全法，並據稱將向香港派駐中國安全部隊，以執行該命令的決定。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的行為將香港自治推至崩潰的邊緣，違反了中國政府在1984年簽署的國際條約《中英聯合聲明》下所承擔的職責。香港過去一年的政治動盪，是香港政府和中國政府共同造成的後果。這包括不願處理香港人民的合法請願，以及未能製止警察對和平抗議者的過度暴力。<br />\n<br />\n維持一個自由開放的香港，符合美利堅合眾國與中華人民共和國兩國的利益。我們呼籲，中國政府止步囂張、改弦易轍，並履行其國際義務，保護香港的自治，也保護香港人民的權利和自由。此外，特朗普政府應根據《香港人權與民主法案》的授權，領導全球聯盟，來保護美國的利益並支持香港人。如果中國政府拒絕撤回破壞香港自治的計劃，美國必須重新評估與香港的關係。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cecc-statement-on-hong-kong/5432780.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fcecc-statement-on-hong-kong%2F5432780.html&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=9e513461\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cecc-statement-on-hong-kong/5432780.html</a>"},{"pid":"a441238fb7b8c56498c404950e469811a034e8a5","tid":2031464,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6340f5d89c949cb10fb42dfed0a3ae4836b118db","tid":2031464,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"制裁777制裁689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7a761d99b493d8a016b45a9ac14963ba44898e","tid":2031464,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a56eb9605ba89279cf0a05c91d68446ec910fe38","tid":2031464,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"唔好退呀支那<br />\n香港獨立靠你ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73a4f53776d126f31185cba3219f64362e1b757","tid":2031464,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a388693629edcfc756a2b3ceef05cf04a2c21bc3","tid":2031464,"uid":120918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"支那共產黨 你唔好撚縮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc8b9eeb75fc2c37840b35418fa8e83808f999b","tid":2031464,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"支那狗開戰啦，淆底呀"},{"pid":"cb3d5f33c42165a8a2b03389b7936f31a483e179","tid":2031464,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a56eb9605ba89279cf0a05c91d68446ec910fe38","tid":2031464,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"唔好退呀支那<br />\n香港獨立靠你ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"共產黨，今次我撑你。"},{"pid":"7b09d885eb5d13ab015d050198ca365cf0d0c0d7","tid":2031464,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"家陣你當 Mr. Highly Tight (緊爽哥) and Mrs. Hua Dama (華大媽) 係流架 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}